{"id":1565358,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"神奈川县出身。初中2年级时在朋友的支援下开始对声优产生兴趣。\n\n在PONY CANYON的第2回PONYCAN声之种试音中获得审查员奖励赏（在当时使用rimyu的名义），并由此声优出道。\n\n历经PONY CANYON ARTISTS之后，隶属于SWALLOW事务所。\n\n2016年，首次出演电影动画《玻璃花与毁坏的世界》，同时也是首次担任主役角色。\n\n同年，以电视动画《干支魂》的广播与村川梨衣丶松井惠理子取得第二回动画广播奖中的「最搞笑广播奖」。\n\n2017年3月31日离开SWALLOW事务所，次日加入m&i事务所。","name":"花守由美里","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Yumiri Hanamori (花守 ゆみり, Hanamori Yumiri, September 29, 1997) is a Japanese voice actress from Kanagawa. She is affiliated with m&i.","name":"Yumiri Hanamori","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","iso_639_1":"hi","name":"हिन्दी","english_name":"Hindi","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"神奈川县出身。初中2年级时在朋友的支援下开始对声优产生兴趣。\n\n在PONY CANYON的第2回PONYCAN声之种试音中获得审查员奖励赏（在当时使用rimyu的名义），并由此声优出道。\n\n历经PONY CANYON ARTISTS之后，隶属于SWALLOW事务所。\n\n2016年，首次出演电影动画《玻璃花与毁坏的世界》，同时也是首次担任主役角色。\n\n同年，以电视动画《干支魂》的广播与村川梨衣丶松井惠理子取得第二回动画广播奖中的「最搞笑广播奖」。\n\n2017年3月31日离开SWALLOW事务所，次日加入m&i事务所。","name":"花守由美里","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"하나모리 유미리","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"花守ゆみり","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yumiri Hanamori","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Yumiri Hanamori (花守 ゆみり, Hanamori Yumiri, 29 de septiembre de 1997) es una actriz de doblaje japonesa de Kanagawa. Está afiliada a m&i.","name":"Yumiri Hanamori","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","da